'''小RNA'''（{{lang|en|small RNA}}，簡稱'''sRNA'''）泛指长度小于200个[[核苷酸|核苷酸]]（nt）的[[RNA|RNA]]分子，多為[[非编码RNA|非编码RNA]]（ncRNA）<ref name="PeshevaDimitrov2012">{{cite book|author1=Margarita Pesheva|author2=Martin Dimitrov|title=Carcinogen|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vOOZDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA121|year=2012|publisher=BoD – Books on Demand|isbn=978-953-51-0658-6|page=121}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Storz|first1=G|title=An expanding universe of noncoding RNAs.|journal=Science|year= 2002|volume=296|issue=5571|pages=1260–3|pmid=12016301|doi=10.1126/science.1072249}}</ref>。[[真核生物|真核生物]]中此類RNA經常可與{{tsl|en|Argonaute|Argonaute|Ago}}等蛋白結合以進行[[RNA干擾|RNA干擾]]，抑制其他基因[[mRNA|mRNA]]的表現。小RNA的種類包括[[微小RNA|微小RNA]]（miRNA）、[[小干扰RNA|小干扰RNA]]（siRNA，包含[[tasiRNA|tasiRNA]]<ref name="Vazquez_2004">{{cite journal | vauthors = Vazquez F, Vaucheret H, Rajagopalan R, Lepers C, Gasciolli V, Mallory AC, Hilbert JL, Bartel DP, Crété P | title = Endogenous trans-acting siRNAs regulate the accumulation of Arabidopsis mRNAs | journal = Mol. Cell | volume = 16 | issue = 1 | pages = 69–79 |date=October 2004 | pmid = 15469823 | doi = 10.1016/j.molcel.2004.09.028 }}</ref>）、[[piRNA|piwi作用RNA]]（piRNA，包含[[rasiRNA|rasiRNA]]<ref name="Klattenhoff">{{cite journal | vauthors = Klattenhoff C, Theurkauf W | title = Biogenesis and germline functions of piRNAs | journal = Development | volume = 135 | issue = 1 | pages = 3–9 | year= 2008 | pmid = 18032451 | doi = 10.1242/dev.006486 }}</ref>）<ref name="MeiWang2015">{{cite journal|last1=Mei|first1=Yuping|last2=Wang|first2=Yuyan|last3=Kumari|first3=Priti|last4=Shetty|first4=Amol Carl|last5=Clark|first5=David|last6=Gable|first6=Tyler|last7=MacKerell|first7=Alexander D.|last8=Ma|first8=Mark Z.|last9=Weber|first9=David J.|last10=Yang|first10=Austin J.|last11=Edelman|first11=Martin J.|last12=Mao|first12=Li|title=A piRNA-like small RNA interacts with and modulates p-ERM proteins in human somatic cells|journal=Nature Communications|volume=6|issue=1|year=2015|issn=2041-1723|doi=10.1038/ncomms8316}}</ref>、[[小核RNA|小核RNA]]（snRNA）、[[小核仁RNA|小核仁RNA]]（snoRNA）<ref name="Morgado2020">{{cite journal|last1=Morgado|first1=Lionel|title=Diversity and types of small RNA|year=2020|pages=37–47|doi=10.1016/B978-0-12-817112-7.00002-X}}</ref>、[[小卡哈氏體RNA|小卡哈氏體RNA]]（scaRNA）、[[tsRNA|tsRNA]]（衍生自[[tRNA|tRNA]]的小RNA）和[[srRNA|srRNA]]（衍生自[[核糖體RNA|rRNA]]的小RNA）<ref name="pmid30720712">{{cite journal| author=Lambert M, Benmoussa A, Provost P| title=Small Non-Coding RNAs Derived From Eukaryotic Ribosomal RNA. | journal=Noncoding RNA | year= 2019 | volume= 5 | issue= 1 | pages=  | pmid=30720712 | doi=10.3390/ncrna5010016 | pmc=6468398 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=30720712  }} </ref>等。現有{{tsl|en|MicroRNA sequencing|miRNA定序}}等{{le|次世代定序|next-generation sequencing}}技術專門用來偵測細胞中的小RNA<ref>{{cite journal|last=Lu|first=C|author2=Tej, SS |author3=Luo, S |author4=Haudenschild, CD |author5=Meyers, BC |author6= Green, PJ |title=Elucidation of the small RNA component of the transcriptome.|journal=Science|date=Sep 2, 2005|volume=309|issue=5740|pages=1567–9|pmid=16141074|doi=10.1126/science.1114112|url=https://semanticscholar.org/paper/1f02a6fb1791345e4187fbe22d46b385d9a7119e}}</ref><ref name="RubyJan2006">{{cite journal|last1=Ruby|first1=J. Graham|last2=Jan|first2=Calvin|last3=Player|first3=Christopher|last4=Axtell|first4=Michael J.|last5=Lee|first5=William|last6=Nusbaum|first6=Chad|last7=Ge|first7=Hui|last8=Bartel|first8=David P.|title=Large-Scale Sequencing Reveals 21U-RNAs and Additional MicroRNAs and Endogenous siRNAs in C. elegans|journal=Cell|volume=127|issue=6|year=2006|pages=1193–1207|issn=0092-8674|doi=10.1016/j.cell.2006.10.040|pmid=17174894}}</ref>。許多小RNA與數種[[癌症|癌症]]等疾病有關<ref name="WuLu2011">{{cite journal|last1=Wu|first1=Qian|last2=Lu|first2=Zuhong|last3=Li|first3=Hailing|last4=Lu|first4=Jiafeng|last5=Guo|first5=Li|last6=Ge|first6=Qinyu|title=Next-Generation Sequencing of MicroRNAs for Breast Cancer Detection|journal=Journal of Biomedicine and Biotechnology|volume=2011|year=2011|pages=1–7|issn=1110-7243|doi=10.1155/2011/597145|pmid=21716661|pmc=3118289}}</ref>。

[[細菌|細菌]]也具有許多小RNA（[[細菌小RNA|細菌小RNA]]），可與其他RNA或蛋白質結合，有調控基因表現，代謝、感染毒力、對環境反應與影響細胞結構等諸多功能<ref name="pmid19007416">{{cite journal|author=Vogel J|date=January 2009|title=A rough guide to the non-coding RNA world of Salmonella|journal=Mol. Microbiol.|volume=71|issue=1|pages=1–11|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2958.2008.06505.x|pmid=19007416}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|last=Felden|first=Brice|last2=Vandenesch|first2=François|last3=Bouloc|first3=Philippe|last4=Romby|first4=Pascale|date=2011-03-10|title=The Staphylococcus aureus RNome and Its Commitment to Virulence|journal=PLoS Pathogens|volume=7|issue=3|doi=10.1371/journal.ppat.1002006|issn=1553-7366|pmc=3053349|pmid=21423670|page=e1002006}}</ref>。

